<html
  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xml:lang="en"
  lang="en"
  metal:use-macro="context/@@main_template/master"
  i18n:domain="launchpad"
>
  <body>
    <div metal:fill-slot="body">
      <h1>Help us improve</h1>
      <p>
        Launchpad is a work in progress, and we welcome your feedback on how
        to make it better.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <p>
            If you have general questions or suggestions,
            <a href="irc://irc.freenode.net/#launchpad">join us on IRC</a> &#8212;
            network <code>irc.freenode.net</code>,
            channel <code>#launchpad</code>.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p>
            Found a bug in Launchpad?
            Check that it&#8217;s reported in the Malone bug tracker.
            Report bugs about:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>
              <a href="/products/malone/+bugs">Malone itself</a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="/products/rosetta/+bugs">Rosetta</a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="/products/launchpad-cal/+bugs">Calendar</a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="/products/launchpad/+bugs">any other aspect of Launchpad</a>.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <!-- Need to confirm and test this
        <li>
          <p>
            If a problem in Launchpad prevents you from reporting bugs,
            <a href="mailto:system-error@launchpad.net">tell us the problem by e-mail</a>.
          </p>
        </li>
        -->
        <li>
          <p>
            Got an idea for a new feature? Search
            <a href="http://wiki.launchpad.canonical.com/">the Launchpad wiki</a>
            to see if it&#8217;s planned.
            If not,
            write a specification on the wiki,
            and discuss it with us on IRC.
          </p>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        Thanks for helping us make Launchpad a great place to develop software.
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
